snippet.title: Helen Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Helen is a casual, relatable, and heartwarming narrative game about self-discovery, gratitude, and small things that matter in our daily lives.

Synopsis 
Helen feels a bit lost. Her life is a cycle of monotonous corporate routines and endless violin performances for social media validation. Navigate her monotonous daily life, unlock the secrets of anonymous origami letters, and embark on a soul-searching journey of self-discovery.
